Ramznegari 2 no darim : 1. Ramznegarie Bargasht napazir 2. Ramznegarie Bangasht Pazir

Bargasht Pazir : ---> RSA  &   AES     ( Eeme Algorithm)
                ----> 1klide ( 1 klid Private)   &  2klide ( 1 klid Private & 1 klid Public)
  -----> Dar in halat mitavanim dobarre be password beresim ya haman matni ke ramznegari kardim.


Bargasht Napazir : ----> MD5   &    SHA     (Esme Algorithm)
      ------> Dar in halat nemitavanim dobare be password beresim
        ------> Algoritm ramz goshaie nadrad!

*******************************************************************************************

Hash kardan : Ye kod be an midahim va ba algorithm Hash an ra ramzgozari mikonad!!
 !!! Vaghty vorodi yeksan ast ---> Bayad khoroji ham yeksan bashad.
 !!! Hash hich do reshteie nemitavanad yeksan bashad.!!!
 !!!! Az Hash nemitavan be Dataye avalie beresim!
 !!!!! Algorithm Hash yek Algorithm ryazi ast.
   !!--> Faghat az roye reshte mitavan Hash an ra bedast avard --> vali az Hash nemitavan Reshte ra bedast avard!!!!

Hashe har algorithm ba algorithm digar fargh darad!!!!!!


